    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a museum-grade A80 Supra, retaining its original 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six and Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is meticulously preserved in factory configuration, featuring the original sequential turbocharger setup and unmolested ECU mapping. The chassis retains all factory VIN tags and exhibits zero signs of oxidation or structural fatigue. Recent preventative maintenance includes a complete timing belt service, valve clearance inspection, and a fluid refresh using Getrag-specific lubricants. The Torsen limited-slip differential and double-wishbone suspension components perform to factory-new tolerances, ensuring the precise handling characteristics this platform is renowned for. A rare, turn-key opportunity for the technical purist.",
